{"tid":2141170,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★內地炒家斷供　多個豪宅物業淪銀主","createTime":"2020-08-05T12:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T05:11:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"59896c620b2d0fec650a26d056175d3be7ece9c1","tid":2141170,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:58:36.000Z","msg":"樓市表現反覆，有早年以高價狂掃本港豪宅的內地炒家，疫情下資金鏈斷裂，持有的多個單位淪為銀主盤。其中，何文田皓畋一個兩房戶，亦淪為銀主盤，銀行推出市場放售叫價1,700萬元，物業三年間貶值230多萬元。<br />\n<br />\n專攻豪宅 持貨不足三年<br />\n<br />\n據市場消息知，<span class=\"xx-large\">許氏為內地炒家，兩、三年前於本港新盤市場上斥逾億元掃貨</span>，專攻豪宅，如何文田皓畋、北角柏蔚山、何文田天鑄等，惟近日多個單位先後淪為銀主盤，一般持貨不足3年，連額外印花稅（SSD）也未鬆綁。其中，北角柏蔚山3座低層戶，今年年中以2,160萬元沽出，較2018年月購入價以2,861.2萬元，兩年間貶值701萬元，跌幅達25%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/507174/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%82%92%E5%AE%B6%E6%96%B7%E4%BE%9B-%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD%E6%B7%AA%E9%8A%80%E4%B8%BB-%E7%9A%93%E7%95%8B%E8%9D%95%E8%AE%93230%E8%90%AC%E6%B1%82%E5%94%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F507174%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2582%2592%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2596%25B7%25E4%25BE%259B-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2580%258B%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25AE%2585%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%25B7%25AA%25E9%258A%2580%25E4%25B8%25BB-%25E7%259A%2593%25E7%2595%258B%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25AE%2593230%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%2594%25AE&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=4174ddfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/507174/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%82%92%E5%AE%B6%E6%96%B7%E4%BE%9B-%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD%E6%B7%AA%E9%8A%80%E4%B8%BB-%E7%9A%93%E7%95%8B%E8%9D%95%E8%AE%93230%E8%90%AC%E6%B1%82%E5%94%AE</a>"},{"pid":"c5b0154df8359ea7b8d12d6f15ac70869c39a56d","tid":2141170,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"